<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[[الحاء والراء]</span>]<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">* شَعَرٌ رِبَحْلٌ ورَجُلٌ رِبَحْلٌ:</span> طَوِيْلٌ،<span class="c5"> وثَوْبٌ كذلك:</span> واسِعٌ.<span class="c5"> وجارِيَةٌ رِبَحْلَةٌ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>تارَّةٌ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">* احْرَنْبَى الكَلْبُ احْرِنْبَاءً:</span> إِذا ازْبَأرَّ،<span class="c5"> والرَّجُلُ:</span> إِذا تَهَيَّأ للغَضَبِ والشَّرِّ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">والاحْرِنْبَاءُ:</span> الاتِّسَاعُ في المَكانِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">والمُحْرَنْبي:</span> الشّاخِصُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">*أتانا في حَنْبَرَةِ قُرٍّ شَديدٍ:</span> أي في شِدَّةِ البَرْدِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>